---
title: Sriracha-Peanut Kung Pao Double Tofu with Jasmine Rice and Veggies
description: This ode to kung pao, an American-Chinese classic, is recreated to be plant-based from top to bottom. Tender tofu chunks are fried until just crispy, then tossed in a sweet and tangy peanut sauce. Crisp veggies and fragrant steamed rice stand by!
